SELECT userid, applicationid, actor, from_status, substatuses
FROM status_update
WHERE to_status = 'DATASIGNS_REJECTED' AND (substatuses like '%FOIR%' or substatuses like '%MCA_NOT_FOUND%' or substatuses like '%LLP_AND_PARTNERSHIP%' or substatuses like '%PROPRIETORSHIP%')
